OL,5, A heart surgeon says he "probably saved
OL,6, the life" of a baby by carrying out a  
OL,7, "world-first" operation using stem     
OL,8, cells from placentas.                  
OL,10,FProfessor Massimo Caputo from the      
OL,11,FBristol Heart Institute used pioneering
OL,12,Fstem cell "scaffolding" to correct baby
OL,13,FFinley's heart defect.                 
OL,15,FHe hopes to develop the technology so  
OL,16,Fchildren born with congenital cardiac  
OL,17,Fdisease won't need as many operations. 
OL,19,FFinley, now two, is "now a happy       
OL,20,Fgrowing little boy".                   
